| Specification Type           | Specification                                                                                                                                                                                      | Reason                                                     | Testing Method                                    |
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Overall Structure            | The video must be split into 3 main parts: Introduction, Presentation of the Learning Process, Conclusion                                                                                           | Ensures the video is logically organized and easy to follow| Review the video to confirm it adheres to this structure |
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Introduction                 | The introduction should clearly state the purpose of the video, introduce the AI model, and explain the objectives and structure of the video                                                       | Provides context and sets viewer expectations              | Watch the introduction segment for completeness and clarity |
|------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------/-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Learning Process Presentation| Split into three parts for each environment: Baseline Performance, Learning Process and Progressive Improvement, Final Performance                                                                  | Demonstrates the AI’s progression in different environments| Check that each environment is presented in these three parts |
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Baseline Performance         | Show initial performance without any training, including metrics like time to target (in seconds), number of collisions, and percentage accuracy of hitting the target                              | Provides a benchmark for measuring improvement             | Compare baseline performance metrics with later stages |
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Learning Process             | Document the AI's training process, showing stages of improvement with metrics such as reduction in time to target (in seconds), decrease in number of collisions, and increase in percentage accuracy. Explain key changes and strategies employed during training (e.g., adjustment of learning rates, exploration/exploitation balance) | Illustrates how the AI learns and adapts| Ensure the video includes clear annotations of iterative improvements |
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Final Performance            | Demonstrate the AI’s performance after training, highlighting key achievements with metrics like final time to target (in seconds), number of collisions (aiming for zero), and percentage accuracy (aiming for close to 70%)                         | Showcases the effectiveness of the training process        | Compare final performance metrics to baseline metrics |
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Objective Statement          | Clearly state the objective of each iteration, such as “The objective for this iteration is to reduce the time to target by 20% while maintaining or improving accuracy and minimizing collisions.”   | Ensures viewers understand the goals of each iteration     | Review each iteration to ensure objectives are clearly stated |
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Visual Clarity               | Use high-quality visuals and clear visual cues (such as highlights, arrows, and captions) to point out important aspects                                                                             | Enhances understanding and engagement                      | Watch for visual quality and clarity                     |
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Narration and Commentary     | Provide clear, engaging commentary throughout the video to explain what's happening, avoiding technical jargon or explaining it concisely                                                            | Keeps viewers informed and engaged                         | Listen to commentary for clarity and engagement           |
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Engagement                   | Include engaging visual and audio elements such as background music, animations, and smooth transitions                                                                                            | Maintains viewer interest                                  | Evaluate viewer engagement and feedback               |
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Performance Metrics          | Highlight initial and final performance metrics with visual aids like graphs or charts, showing changes in time to target, number of collisions, and accuracy percentage                              | Demonstrates the AI’s improvement in a clear manner         | Check the use and clarity of performance metrics and visual aids |
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Technical Accuracy           | Ensure all technical information presented is accurate and up to date, possibly including brief interviews or quotes from experts                                                                     | Maintains credibility and informativeness                  | Fact-check all technical content                       |
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Conclusion                   | Summarize the AI model’s journey and achievements, discuss potential future improvements and applications, and invite feedback                                                                       | Provides closure and future insights                       | Watch the conclusion segment for completeness and effectiveness |
